data.description: Meticulously maintained ranch style home! Beautiful curb appeal & move-in ready. Offers three generous sized bedrooms, a renovated bathroom and new carpets throughout (hardwood floors underneath). Large kitchen with ample countertop space & stainless-steel appliances. Open floor concept joins large living room to formal dining room with sliding doors. Perfect for entertaining! Many upgrades within the past 10 years include - kitchen/appliances, roof, siding, windows/doors, heating system & 200 amp electric. Plenty of storage/closet space with pull-down stairs to full attic. Fully fenced landscaped backyard with trex deck & patio. Minutes from popular Venetian Beach, Tanner Park, LIRR, shopping and restaurants.
